      "start_time": 267,
      "end_time": 267,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "[inaudible 00:04:27]."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "_uncategorized_",
          "tag": "Brenda Dixon Gottschild"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "dc1d2210-cfac-46e6-a3c0-8787a8f0ea1e"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 267,
      "end_time": 271,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "She's also like-"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "8940670a-cf17-4cca-8ced-f3185fb7663b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 271,
      "end_time": 275,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yes."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "_uncategorized_",
          "tag": "Brenda Dixon Gottschild"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "2d0750bc-44df-401c-8d29-a327ae200c40"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 275,
      "end_time": 282,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "You know, you're working with an elder, but at the same time I was like, \"I want to be you when I grow up.\" Like, I just ... The vitality-"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "2e98cb1c-76f9-43ff-a0b2-c26f261bd4bb"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 282,
      "end_time": 285,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yes. Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "_uncategorized_",
          "tag": "Brenda Dixon Gottschild"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "c3bf4bc3-26ca-4321-b63b-eae9df39e2b9"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 285,
      "end_time": 317,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Then, to learn the stuff and then have it be ... Sometimes, there's this one moment in the day where I just flip over. She's like, \"Okay, flip over.\" And I did, and she'd laugh because I really like ... She's like, \"Oh, that's funny.\" I felt like we ... It became playful, which the first couple of days, I think, because it was just the time to make it work."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "b8271c05-8319-4ec5-aeac-5ba5de8eb07e"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 317,
      "end_time": 318,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "_uncategorized_",
          "tag": "Brenda Dixon Gottschild"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "d5a5e822-93ab-4d28-8a31-db8259a9a70d"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 318,
      "end_time": 325,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "When the play sort of came into it, that's when I really started [crosstalk 00:05:23], and that was exciting."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "75fb6b0b-893c-4788-993d-73c869aaafa6"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 325,
      "end_time": 358,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "What's so nice is that it does have a lightness about it. In contrast to ... You need that with the David Rousseve piece that you've got to let us know. Of course, that one David Rousseve piece, of course, is not all of David Rousseve, but for this project to let us indeed know the no boundaries of the black dancing endeavor. You know? Yeah."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "_uncategorized_",
          "tag": "Brenda Dixon Gottschild"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "f7b425b0-0b7d-4138-97d7-7d7cfbac3650"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 358,
      "end_time": 368,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Yeah, that's why tonight we have How to Watch A Modern Dance concert [crosstalk 00:06:05]. Were you able to make your-"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Gesel Mason",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "98a7bbd2-ec75-4fb8-9971-3ac33167d164"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 368,
      "end_time": 368,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "I did, yes."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "tag": "Speaker 3",
          "category": "People"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "ce9b1c44-ff0c-45f8-b74d-526d70c7d73c"
